Privacy Policy  

What data is saved?
- Username and encrypted password are saved, not even the administrator can find out the users password.
- Anything users create ill be saved, like todo-lists and tasks.

Why is the data saved?
- This is to give users the possibility of saving multiple todo-lists to use for their on benefit.

How is the data used?
- Users data can connenct them with eachother, for example sharing todo-lists.
- Users can check tasks as done or urgent to interact and change their saved data (todo-lists).
- Developers will use the unique ID of users account to make this webb service possible.

How do you remove data?
- If you'd like to remove all data we have on you, just delete your account and all history, lists and tasks, will be removed